Content.Name: Company configuration backup
Content.ShortDescription: Periodically backup Integray company configuration and send it via email
Content.Description:
# Company configuration backup

This template periodically downloads Integray configuration of specified company and sends it to your email. Template is executed every day at **7:00 AM**.

## Template configuration

Configure this template


### Set Integray address

Copy URL address from browser URL bar and remove everything starting with `/` symbol (which results to ie. `https://example.integray.app`)

### Provide settings from company you wish to backup

 * Open your company detail and copy `Slug` value, paste it to **Company slug** variable of this template

![](data:image/png;base64, =456x450)

 * Scroll down to **Remote Control** section and
  * Make sure you have ``Allow sharing remote config transfer`` checked
  * ``Allow control`` is set to **Token**
  * Copy `Remote control token` and paste it to **Company Token** variable of this template
 
![](data:image/png;base64, =456x450)

### Send email

 * Fill **Backup Email** template variable with your email address
 * Fill **Sendgrid token** template variable with [SendGrid API key](https://docs.sendgrid.com/ui/account-and-settings/api-keys)
